but you have to help me.

397
00:27:09,463 --> 00:27:11,548
No, I don't. Why?

398
00:27:11,632 --> 00:27:15,135
Well, my legs, which normally
would be classified as lethal weapons,

399
00:27:15,219 --> 00:27:16,345
